messages.content: That is a nice gun you got there
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Grenadier-+whbpZAuyk

messages.content: Thanks man. I've always had a thing for SMGs. Gets the job done up close and personal, ya know? How's your gear treating you?
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_polish_PRIVATE_Looter(SMG)-de3YSZo80s0

messages.content: I got a GL 6.5mm assault rifle. Pretty decent, splits the enemy into many little pieces
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Grenadier-+whbpZAuyk

messages.content: 'Ah, the good old split 'em up tactic. Sometimes simple is best.'
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_polish_PRIVATE_Looter(SMG)-de3YSZo80s0

messages.content: 'So, what brings you to Air Station Mike-26?'
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_polish_PRIVATE_Looter(SMG)-de3YSZo80s0

messages.content: We got reports of looters in the are, I am just investigating
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Grenadier-+whbpZAuyk

messages.content: 'Looters, huh? Sounds like my kind of people. If you need backup, I'm your guy.'
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_polish_PRIVATE_Looter(SMG)-de3YSZo80s0

messages.content: I am here to shoot or arrest looters, not help them
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Grenadier-+whbpZAuyk

messages.content: 'Fair enough, just offering my services. Let me know if you need anything.'
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_polish_PRIVATE_Looter(SMG)-de3YSZo80s0

messages.content: No, I'm not a looter. I'm with the INDEPENDENT faction, but I only take what I need to survive. I don't harm innocent people.
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_polish_PRIVATE_Looter(SMG)-de3YSZo80s0

messages.content: 'Well, if you need any help tracking down those looters, let me know. I know the area pretty well.'
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_polish_PRIVATE_Looter(SMG)-de3YSZo80s0
